1. Allowed use

You may view, study, build, flash, and modify this project for personal,
educational, hobby, repair, and non-commercial use.

You may make a small number of copies for your own personal devices or for
non-commercial testing.

2. Prohibited use

Without prior written permission from the copyright holder, you may not:

- sell this project, firmware, PCB designs, documentation, or derived works,
- sell devices, kits, PCBs, firmware images, or services based on this project,
- use this project or any substantial part of it in a commercial product,
- use this project or any substantial part of it for paid installation,
  manufacturing, support, consulting, or similar commercial activity,
- redistribute modified versions in a way that suggests they are official,
- remove copyright notices, license notices, or attribution,
- claim authorship of this project or derived work based on it.

3. Redistribution

Redistribution of the original or modified source is allowed only for
non-commercial purposes and only if this license, copyright notice, and clear
attribution to the original project are included.

Modified versions must be clearly marked as modified and must not use the
original project name in a way that suggests endorsement by the copyright holder.

4. Author rights

The copyright holder reserves the right to use, manufacture, sell, license,
and commercially distribute this project, firmware, PCB designs, documentation,
finished devices, and derived works.

The non-commercial restrictions in this license apply to third parties, not to
the copyright holder.

